<rdf:Description
    rdf:about="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1185"
    trackback:ping="http://www.notapathetic.com/cgi-bin/trackback.cgi/1185"
    dc:title="The party system represents a conflict..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1185"
    dc:description="The party system represents a conflict of interest,  My MP as my representative should reflect the opinions of myself and my fellow constituents over and above those of his/her party but the use of party whips ensures..."
